msgctxt "talk00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Oh, <2.pa>pardon me...<3.pa> I was lost in "
"thought.<4.pa><5.ra><6.so>You've heard of the <7.se_co>Great "
"Fairy<8.re_co>, right?<9.pa>\n"
"The one from all those old stories?<10.pa>\n"
"\n"
"<11.so>Well, they're not just stories! I believe\n"
"the <12.se_co>Great Fairy <13.re_co>is real! And I'm on a\n"
"journey to find her.\n"
"<14.so>There's a tower just beyond the\n"
"<15.se_co>Tabantha Great Bridge<16.re_co>.\n"
"\n"
"They say that if you go to the top and\n"
"look at the ground sometime in the\n"
"afternoon...\n"
"<17.se_co>The tower's shadow will point <18.re_co>to the\n"
"<19.se_co>Great Fairy<20.re_co>'s fountain!\n"
"\n"
"After hearing that legend, I decided to\n"
"find out for myself. But now I'm stuck\n"
"here at this stable because... Well..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
#. 3: sound
#. 4: set_colour (blue)
#. 5: reset_colour
msgctxt "talk01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>No matter how hard I try, I just know I'll\n"
"never be able to climb that tower.<2.pa>\n"
"\n"
"<3.so>And to think, I even saved up all my\n"
"rupees as an offering for the <4.se_co>Great Fairy<5.re_co>."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
#. 3: pause (long)
#. 4: raw
#. 5: sound
#. 6: set_colour (blue)
#. 7: reset_colour
#. 8: choice
msgctxt "talk02"
msgid ""
"<1.so>But you...<2.pa> You look like you could climb\n"
"that tower without breaking a sweat!<3.pa><4.ra><5.so>Would you be "
"willing to make an offering\n"
"of rupees to the <6.se_co>Great Fairy<7.re_co> on my\n"
"behalf?<8.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: set_colour (red)
#. 4: reset_colour
msgctxt "talk03"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Oh, thank you!<2.pa> Here, take the <3.se_co>500\n"
"rupees <4.re_co>I saved up. It's my life savings!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: text_size
#. 2: sound
#. 3: set_colour (grey)
#. 4: reset_colour
#. 5: text_size
msgctxt "talk04"
msgid ""
"<1.te_si><2.so><3.se_co>So please don't just go running off with it, "
"OK?<4.re_co><5.te_si>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: raw
#. 4: sound
msgctxt "talk05"
msgid ""
"<1.so>You really won't help?<2.pa> That's too bad,\n"
"but I guess I can't blame you...<3.ra><4.so>I'll be here if you change "
"your mind.\n"
"So come talk if you want to help me\n"
"out later!"
msgstr ""

