"<1.so><2.se_co>The shadow of the tower just beyond the<3.re_co>\n"
"<4.se_co>Tabantha Great Bridge <5.re_co>will point to the\n"
"<6.se_co>Great Fairy<7.re_co>'s fountain in the afternoon.\n"
"It'll be pretty hard to see the shadow in\n"
"this rain...\n"
"\n"
"But still, I'm counting on you to make\n"
"that offering to the <8.se_co>Great Fairy<9.re_co>!"
