msgid ""
"<1.so>All right! Thank you! Looks like asking\n"
"you was a good call after all.\n"
"\n"
"<2.so>So that means you met the <3.se_co>Great Fairy<4.re_co>,\n"
"huh? Man, I'm so jealous...\n"
"\n"
"<5.so>But hey, at least you got to meet her!\n"
